Please only output code and not your natural language commentary.", 'Can you add logging support to the `move_funds` function? It would be helpful to log each transfer attempt, including the user ID, source and destination accounts, amount, and whether the transfer was successful or failed due to authorization issues. This will help in auditing and tracking fund movements.
